程序包 org.giiwa.dao.sql

接口 SqlVisitor<T>

类型参数:
T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
所有超级接口:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
所有已知实现类:
SqlBaseVisitor
public interface SqlVisitor<T> extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by SqlParser.
